#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:8
#, python-format
msgid ""
"I'm %(name)s, your SUMO Community Manager. On behalf of the Customer Experience team, I'd love to thank you for registering as a contributor at SUMO a.k.a. <a "
"href=\"%(home_url)s\">SUpport.MOzilla.org</a>. We're so excited you've joined us! Mozilla wouldn't be what it is today without the passionate contributions from people like you."
msgstr ""
"Sym %(name)s, waš manager zhromadźenstwa SUMO. W mjenje teama za dožiwjenja kupcow bych so wam rady dźakował, zo sće so jako sobuskutkowar na SUMO alias <a "
"href=\"%(home_url)s\">SUpport.MOzilla.org</a> zregistrował. Wjeselimy so jara, zo sće so nam přidružił! Mozilla njeby to był, štož je dźensa, bjez pasioněrowanych přinoškow ludźi kaž wy."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:14
#, python-format
msgid ""
"On behalf of the Customer Experience team, we'd love to thank you for registering as a contributor at SUMO a.k.a. <a href=\"%(home_url)s\">SUpport.MOzilla.org</a>. We're so excited you've joined us!"
" Mozilla wouldn't be what it is today without the passionate contributions from people like you."
msgstr ""
"W mjenje teama za dožiwjenja kupcow bychmy so wam rady dźakowali, zo sće so jako sobuskutkowar na SUMO alias <a href=\"%(home_url)s\">SUpport.MOzilla.org</a> zregistrował. Wjeselimy so jara, zo sće "
"so nam přidružił! Mozilla njeby to był, štož je dźensa, bjez pasioněrowanych přinoškow ludźi kaž wy."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:21 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:23
msgid "To help you get started, here are a few essentials:"
msgstr "Zo bychmy wam pomhali započeć, tu su někotre wažne wěcy:"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:26 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:28
msgid "Know the basics"
msgstr "Zeznajće so ze zakładami"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:28
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Before diving in, please take a moment to read our <a href=\"%(cpg_url)s\">Community Participation Guidelines (CPG)</a>. This helps us maintain a safe and positive community experience for all. You "
"can also take <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">this short course</a> to learn more."
msgstr ""
"Prjedy hač započnjeće, bjerće sej wokomik časa, zo byšće naše <a href=\"%(cpg_url)s\">směrnicy za wobdźělenje na zhromadźenstwje (CPG)</a> čitał. To nam pomha, wěste a pozitiwne dožiwjenje "
"zhromadźenstwa za wšěch hladać. Móžeće so tež za <a href=\"%(course_url)s\">tutón krótki kurs</a> zapisać, zo byšće wjace zhonił."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:33 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:40
msgid "Choose how you'd like to contribute"
msgstr "Rozsudźće, kak chceće přinošować"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:35 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:43
msgid "There are 3 ways you can contribute to Mozilla through SUMO:"
msgstr "Su 3 móžnosće, z kotrymiž móžeće Mozilla přez SUMO přinošować:"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:42
#, python-format
msgid "<a href=\"%(url)s\">By answering questions in the Community Forums</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\"%(url)s\">Přez wotmołwy na prašenja w forumach zhromadźenstwa</a>"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:47
#, python-format
msgid "<a href=\"%(url)s\">By improving our help articles in English</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\"%(url)s\">Přez polěpšenje našich nastawkow pomocy w jendźelšćinje</a>"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:52
#, python-format
msgid "<a href=\"%(url)s\">By localizing our help articles into your local language</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\"%(url)s\">Přez přełožowanje našich nastawkow pomocy do swojeje lokalneje rěče</a>"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:58 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:69
msgid "Stay connected and ask for help"
msgstr "Wostańće w zwisku a prošće wo pomoc"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:60 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:72
msgid "Running into a blocker or just want to connect with the others? Don't worry! Here are a few ways to connect with the community and get support:"
msgstr "Storčiće na haćenje abo chceće so prosće z druhimi do zwiska stajić? Žadyn strach! Tu su někotre móžnosće, kak so móžeće ze zhromadźenstwom do zwiska stajić a podpěru dóstać:"

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:67
#, python-format
msgid "<a href=\"%(url)s\">SUMO Matrix room</a>: Join our community chat space to ask quick questions or connect with fellow contributors in real time."
msgstr "<a href=\"%(url)s\">Rum SUMO Matrix</a>: Přistupće četowemu rumej našeho zhromadźenstwa, zo byšće spěšnje prašenja stajił abo druhich sobuskutkowarjow we woprawdźitym času skontaktował."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:72
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">Community Discussions</a>: Participate in ongoing discussion threads or start your own. You can also follow the forum to stay updated on Firefox releases and community "
"announcements."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">Diskusije zhromadźenstwa</a>: Wobdźělće so na diskusijnych nitkach abo startujće swójsku nitku. Móžeće tež forumej sćěhować, zo byšće wo nowych wersijach Firefox a "
"připowědźenjach na běžnym wostał."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:77
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">Community Call</a>: Join us for our regular call at <strong>5 PM UTC on Wednesdays</strong> (typically during <a href=\"%(release_weeks_url)s\">release weeks</a>) to catch up on "
"updates and chat with the team."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">Rozrěč zhromadźenstwa</a>: Přidružće so našej regularnej rozrěči <strong>na srjedach 17:00 hodź. UTC</strong> (zwjetša we <a href=\"%(release_weeks_url)s\">wozjewjenskich "
"tydźenjach</a>), zo bychmy aktualizacije dóstali a z teamom četowali."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:85
#, python-format
msgid "If you ever need help or just want to say hi, feel free to <a href=\"%(pm_url)s\">message me directly on SUMO</a>. I'd love to hear from you!"
msgstr "Jeli hdy pomoc trjebaće abo prosće chceće witaj prajić, sćelće <a href=\"%(pm_url)s\">mi powěsć direktnje na SUMO</a>. Bych so wjeselił, wot was słyšeć!"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:91 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:109
msgid "If you ever need help or just want to say hi, feel free to reach out to the community! We'd love to hear from you!"
msgstr "Jeli hdy pomoc trjebaće abo prosće chceće witaj prajić, wobroćće so na zhromadźenstwo! Bychmy so wjeselili, wot was słyšeć!"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.html:98 kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:116
msgid "Thanks again for being here, and let's keep rocking the helpful web together! 🚀"
msgstr "Dźakujemy so hišće raz za to, zo sće tu a ćěrmy pomocliwy web hromadźe doprědka! 🚀"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:7
#, python-format
msgid ""
"I'm %(name)s, your SUMO Community Manager. On behalf of the Customer Experience team, I'd love to thank you for registering as a contributor at SUMO a.k.a. SUpport.MOzilla.org. We're so excited "
"you've joined us! Mozilla wouldn't be what it is today without the passionate contributions from people like you."
msgstr ""
"Sym %(name)s, waš manager zhromadźenstwa SUMO. W mjenje teama za dožiwjenja kupcow bych so wam rady dźakował, zo sće so jako sobuskutkowar na SUMO alias SUpport.MOzilla.org zregistrował. Wjeselimy "
"so jara, zo sće so nam přidružił! Mozilla njeby to był, štož je dźensa, bjez pasioněrowanych přinoškow ludźi kaž wy."

#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:14
msgid ""
"On behalf of the Customer Experience team, we'd love to thank you for registering as a contributor at SUMO a.k.a. SUpport.MOzilla.org. We're so excited you've joined us! Mozilla wouldn't be what it "
"is today without the passionate contributions from people like you."
msgstr ""
"W mjenje teama za dožiwjenja kupcow bychmy so wam rady dźakowali, zo sće so jako sobuskutkowar na SUMO alias SUpport.MOzilla.org zregistrował. Wjeselimy so jara, zo sće so nam přidružił! Mozilla "
"njeby to był, štož je dźensa, bjez pasioněrowanych přinoškow ludźi kaž wy."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:31
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Before diving in, please take a moment to read our Community Participation Guidelines (CPG)(%(cpg_url)s). This helps us maintain a safe and positive community experience for all. You can also take "
"this short course to learn more."
msgstr ""
"Prjedy hač započnjeće, bjerće sej wokomik časa, zo byšće naše směrnicy za wobdźělenje na zhromadźenstwje (CPG) (%(cpg_url)s) čitał. To nam pomha, wěste a pozitiwne dožiwjenje zhromadźenstwa za wšěch"
" hladać. Móžeće so tež za tutón krótki kurs zapisać, zo byšće wjace zhonił."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:48
msgid "By answering questions in the Community Forums"
msgstr "Přez wotmołwy na prašenja w forumach zhromadźenstwa"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:55
msgid "By improving our help articles in English"
msgstr "Přez polěpšenje našich nastawkow pomocy w jendźelšćinje"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:62
msgid "By localizing our help articles into your local language"
msgstr "Přez přełožowanje našich nastawkow pomocy do swojeje lokalneje rěče"

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:78
msgid "SUMO Matrix room: Join our community chat space to ask quick questions or connect with fellow contributors in real time."
msgstr "Rum SUMO Matrix: Přistupće četowemu rumej našeho zhromadźenstwa, zo byšće spěšnje prašenja stajił abo druhich sobuskutkowarjow we woprawdźitym času skontaktował."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:86
msgid "Community Discussions: Participate in ongoing discussion threads or start your own. You can also follow the forum to stay updated on Firefox releases and community announcements."
msgstr ""
"Diskusije zhromadźenstwa: Wobdźělće so na diskusijnych nitkach abo startujće swójsku nitku. Móžeće tež forumej sćěhować, zo byšće wo nowych wersijach Firefox a připowědźenjach na běžnym wostał."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:95
#, python-format
msgid "Community Call: Join us for our regular call at 5 PM UTC on Wednesdays (%(url)s) (typically during release weeks - %(release_weeks_url)s) to catch up on updates and chat with the team."
msgstr ""
"Rozrěč zhromadźenstwa: Přidružće so našej regularnej rozrěči na srjedach 17:00 hodź. UTC (%(url)s) (zwjetša w wozjewjenskich tydźenjach – %(release_weeks_url)s), zo bychmy aktualizacije dóstali a z "
"teamom četowali."

#. This is an email.  Whitespace matters!
#: kitsune/users/jinja2/users/email/contributor.ltxt:102
msgid "If you ever need help or just want to say hi, feel free to message me directly on SUMO. I'd love to hear from you!"
msgstr "Jeli hdy pomoc trjebaće abo prosće chceće witaj prajić, sćelće mi powěsć direktnje na SUMO. Bych so wjeselił, wot was słyšeć!"

